quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  40,26,"Fir'awana wi'i: Accee mi wara Muusaa, fii yaggingol mo, e no o noddira Joomi makko, fii ha…óugol lam …óum. Min mi haajaaka e …óum. Mi hulu wata o waylu diina mon kan, maa o fe√±√±ina bonnere ka leydi, woni warugol e bonnital."
  40,27,"Nde Fir'awna gaynunoo kammbude, Annabai Muusaa maakani mo: Mi moolorii da…óndiragol Jey…óo lam On, jeyi on, e bone mawnintinanii…óo goonga e gom…óinal, mo gom…óinaa √ëalnde Darngal, e hasboore e lepte ko woni ton."
  40,28,"Gorko goo, gom…óin…óo Allah, jeyaa…óo e yim…ìe fir'awna …ìen, suu…óunoo…óo yim…ìe mun, gom…óinal makko ngal, salii…óo fellitgol ma…ì…ìe warugol Muusa ngol, o wi'i: E on waray gorko mo bonnaa, si wanaa fii o wi'i: Ko Allah woni Joomi am? Hara le o addanii on hujjaaji e …ìannganduyeeji, sembinay…ói goonga makko kan, wiide ko O nulaa…óo Joomi makko? Si tawii ko o fenu…óo, haray lorra fenaande makko nden, ko e makko yantata; si tawii non ko goongu…óo, haray yoga e ko o kammbirani on kon e lepte aduna …óen, he…ìay on. Pellet, Allah fewanataa e goonga, on taw…óo no yawti keeri Allah …óin, fefindii fenaande, baki e Makko, Kanko e Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  40,29,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, laamu no woodani on hanndi, hi…óon fooli e leydi Misra ndin. Kono ko hommbo da…óndata en, e lepte Allah …óen, si …óe arii e men, tuma waru…óen Muusaa? Fir'awna wi'i: Ko feere am nde mi √±aawi nden, jokketee. Mi yi'ii feere warugol Muusaa, fii ha…óugol bone e bonnere. Mi tinndintaa on, si wanaa sawaaba."
  40,30,"Gom…óin…óo on laa…ìani reedu, o wi'itani yim…ìe makko …ìen: min on mi…óo hulani on - si tawii on arii Muusaa e hoore too√±e e jaggitere - lepte, sugu lepte yim…ìe feddeeji …ìen, ha…ìunoo…ìe Nulaa…ìe mun adinoo…ìe, Allah halki …ìe."
  40,31,"Wano mbowka yeddaynoo…ìe fenna Nulaa…ìe …ìen, sugu yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen, e Aadi'en, e Samuuda'en, e arunoo…ìe …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe …ìen. Allah halkirno …ìe, yeddugol ma…ì…ìe fenna Nulaa…ìe …ìen. Allah non faandanaaki jeyaa…ìe …ìen, too√±e. Ko junuubi ma…ì…ìe, O leptirta …ìe, njo…ìdi hawrondindi e golle ma…ì…ìe …óen."
  40,32,"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, min mi…óo hulani on, √ëalnde Darngal: nden √ëalaande, nde yim…ìe …ìen noddindiroyta, sabu …ìadandiral maa jaahu, sikkugol …ìe …óum nafay nden √ëalnde hul…ìiniinde."
  40,33,"√ëalnde huccitiroyton, dugugol, sabu kulol Yiite ngen, hara da…óndoowo on e lepte Allah …óen, alanaa on nden √ëalnde. Kala mo Allah hoyfii fii mun, O …óawi mo gom…óingol, haray fewoowo mo alaa. Tawde ko Allah tun fewnata."